#######
#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;For when one whacking-stick just isnt enough.^reset;

The Grand Armory Mod adds a bunch of new weapon types to random generation all of which use the existing weapon artwork.

Baton - short and quick stick
Cane - medium and quick stick
Club - large, heavy, blunt weapon which stuns
Greataxe - large, heavy, double bladed axe
Greatsword - slightly longer reach than standard broadsword
Mace - light and quick...for a hammer
Greatmace - same but 2h
Quarterstaff - long and quick stick
Shortspear - one handed short-range spear
Armcannon - very fast plasma shot
Longbow - great for hunting
Spellbook - contains arcane magics

spawncodes are as follows:
common- uncommon- rare-
-baton -cane -club -ga -gs -mace -gm -qs -shortspear -ac -lb -gb -sb

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

######
#steam		
######

[h1]For when one whacking-stick just isnt enough.[/h1]

The Grand Armory Mod adds a bunch of new weapon types to random generation all of which use the existing weapon artwork.

Baton - short and quick stick
Cane - medium and quick stick
Club - large, heavy, blunt weapon which stuns
Greataxe - large, heavy, double bladed axe
Greatsword - slower and slightly longer reach than standard broadsword
Mace - light and quick...for a hammer
Greatmace - same but 2h
Quarterstaff - long and quick stick
Shortspear - one handed short-range spear
Armcannon - very fast plasma shot
Longbow - great for hunting
Spellbook - contains arcane magics

spawncodes are as follows:
common- uncommon- rare-
-baton -cane -club -ga -gs -mace -gm -qs -shortspear -ac -lb -gb -sb

Integrated with:
-[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=802382977]Open Armory[/url]
-[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=782921923]Windup Armory Auto[/url]
-[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=782911333]Windup Armory Glow[/url]

Compatibility patches for:
-[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=729480149]Frackin Universe[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=837593165]patch[/url])
-[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=817468961]Melee Aiming[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=837593261]patch[/url])
-[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=760396113]Manufacturer's Touch[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=837593363]patch[/url])
-[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=780877247]Quarterstaff Armory[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=837593510]patch[/url])

Does not work with the [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=783742589]Weapon Assembly[/url] station. Both mods function fine, the Grand Armory weapons are just inconsistent when put into the station.

[url=community.playstarbound.com/threads/124193/]MEGATHREAD[/url]
[url=https://github.com/IsaacHart/sbmod-grandarm/blob/master/CHANGELOG]CHANGELOG[/url]
Alternate downloads can be found on my [url=https://github.com/IsaacHart/sbmod-grandarm/releases/0.6]github.[/url]

